data.description: Stylish 3BR, 2.5BA ranch-style home nestled in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood. Situated near tranquil Sippo Lake, this modern retreat seamlessly blends elegance and functionality. Thoughtfully updated flooring, kitchen, and baths make the home both modern and inviting. Spacious 4-car garage with workshop, heating system, and optional partition is the perfect place for your hobbies, projects, or man-cave . Well-appointed kitchen with quality wood cabinetry makes the home an ideal place to entertain. Master with half-bath en suite provides privacy and convenience. Flexible lower level features bonus rooms that may be easily converted to offices or bedrooms. Newly landscaped yard with plenty of room to grow. Don't miss this opportunity—schedule your showing today!
